Why do I think this FFA for a month will be a good idea?  Because it will shine the light once and for all that rotations are the best option.  The flames, the hatred, that animosity will be crazy.  It will no doubt change the minds of many pro-FFA folks.  That was my reasoning behind it.<br>
<br>
