I apologize folks, as drawing up bad blood was not my intent.<br>
Also, as always, I always post here without consulting my guild.  Never have never will.  My opinions and actions on MT.com are mine alone!!!  Whatever DM's stance on any issue will be made by an officer or guild leader.  And if ya think for one damn minute whining to them about what I say on here is gonna stop me, you need to wake the hell up.  kthx =)<br>
