<br>
It's now getting to the point in the timeline that anyone not already on the list isn't EVER gonna get their epic... EQ2 will be out by then.<br>
<br>
So yes, it screws anyone on the list to go FFA, but it screws any cleric (or epic-less guild for that matter) who isn't already on it by keeping the rotation. No matter how skilled or ambitious or driven a cleric is, they're essentially NEVER gonna get their clicker.<br>
<br>
I remember my own time on the list well, and have always been impressed by the community spirit involved.<br>
<br>
I don't think we should ever go fully FFA, but people should be open to proposals.<br>
